cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on visual odometry and optical flow estimation using deep learning techniques.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of Inertial Measurement Units (IMUs) for pose estimation and the application of the proposed method in robotics.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a self-supervised deep learning network for visual inertial odometry.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for solving a computer vision problem.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the application of the proposed method in a system that involves both visual and inertial sensors.
